# Renaissance / Dashboard shared boundary

**Canonical doc:** [`docs/architect/policy_wiring_surface_map_v1.md`](docs/architect/policy_wiring_surface_map_v1.md) §5.

**Before editing the globbed files:** pull `main`, **announce a lock** on the file/surface, merge, **release lock**.

